                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> Iunoni R<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>g</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">inae Minervae</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Iulianus <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ustos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>rmorum</ex></expan> l<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>eg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> et <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="3"/>Valentina ex vot<supplied reason="lost">o posuerunt</supplied> <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>V<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Über dem Inschriftfeld noch der untere Rest zweier Relieffiguren erhalten (kapitolinische Trias). (B): Kremer; Krüger: Z. 2: [leg(ionis); Z. 4: v(otum?) [s(olverunt?) l(ibentes) m(erito)?]. Betz: Z. 1: r(e)g[ine Minervae]; Z. 5: [------]. Betz; Krüger: Z. 4: vo[to posuerunt]; Hild: Z. 2: [leg(ionis).</p>
            </div>
